names {"rocky tunnel", "tunnel"}
title "A Rocky Tunnel"
descr
"   This tunnel seems to veer off from the rest of the first plane.
The ground you walk and tunnel walls all appear much darker than
those of the entrance to this plane. You notice the darkness is
from the long collection of a smokey resin with an as of yet unknown
cause. The tunnel continues to the west."
flags {UNIT_FL_NO_WEATHER, UNIT_FL_NO_MOB}
